data.description: Come take a look at this lovely fully renovated 3 bedroom ranch sitting a little over an acre lot with lots of mature trees. Recent updates include all new kitchen cabinets and countertops, all new vinyl planking flooring, fresh paint throughout, all new doors & trim, all new electrical panel, new double vanity sink & all new light fixtures! Other updates include roof in 2012, front porch in 2012, windows in 2012, well pump in 2019, Morton water softener in 2016 & 220 amp generator hookup. Full basement ready for finishing touches! Enjoy a large deck for entertaining & barbecuing overlooking a private lot equipped w/ a large pavilion that will be great for picnics or additional storage! Minutes from Rt 70 for an easy commute to downtown Columbus or 10 minutes to Buckeye Lake. SWL schools!
